---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="NexWorker - Der digitale Service-Assistent">

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 transition-all duration-300 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-slate-200" id="navbar">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-20">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
                    <img src="/logo.png" alt="NexWorker" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl" />
                    <span class="font-bold text-xl tracking-tight text-surface">NexWorker</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8">
                    <!-- Lösungen Dropdown -->
                    <div class="relative group">
                        <button class="text-slate-500 hover:text-surface transition-colors font-medium text-sm flex items-center gap-1">
                            Lösungen
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
                        </button>
                        <div class="absolute left-0 mt-2 w-64 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-xl shadow-xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all z-50 p-2">
                            <a href="/wissenssicherung-handwerk" class="block p-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg group/item">
                                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover/item:text-brand transition-colors">Wissenssicherung</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Know-how im Betrieb halten</div>
                            </a>
                            <a href="/beweissicherung-baustelle" class="block p-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg group/item">
                                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover/item:text-brand transition-colors">Beweissicherung</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Rechtssichere Dokumentation</div>
                            </a>
                            <a href="/whatsapp-baudokumentation" class="block p-3 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg group/item">
                                <div class="font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover/item:text-brand transition-colors">WhatsApp Dokumentation</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-slate-400">Dokumentation ohne App</div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#kill-shots" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-surface transition-colors font-medium text-sm">Vorteile</a>
                    <a href="#tagesablauf" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-surface transition-colors font-medium text-sm">Workflow</a>
                    <a href="#preise" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-surface transition-colors font-medium text-sm">Preise</a>
                    <a href="#cta" class="bg-surface hover:bg-surface-light text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-medium text-sm transition-all shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">Demo starten</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Mobile menu button -->
                <div class="md:hidden flex items-center">
                    <button class="text-slate-600 hover:text-surface focus:outline-none">
                        <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-32 relative overflow-hidden clip-diagonal bg-white">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid pointer-events-none z-0"></div>
        
        <!-- Abstract blur -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-40 -mt-40 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-brand-50 opacity-70 blur-[80px] pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
            <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
                
                <!-- Text Content -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-7 gs-reveal-hero mb-16 lg:mb-0">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 font-medium text-xs mb-8 border border-slate-200">
                        <span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand mr-2"></span>
                        Bereit für den europäischen Mittelstand
                    </div>
                    
                    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-surface leading-[1.05]">
                        Weniger Papierkram,<br>
                        <span class="text-brand">mehr Zeit fürs Geschäft.</span>
                    </h1>
                    
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 mb-6 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-normal">
                        BauPVO 2026 compliant – per Sprachnachricht. Keine neue App. NexWorker organisiert Zeiten, Material und Berichte automatisch aus WhatsApp & Telegram.
                    </p>

                    
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                        <a href="#kontakt" class="bg-brand hover:bg-brand-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-medium text-base transition-all shadow-glow hover:shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 text-center flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                            Kostenlos testen
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#tagesablauf" class="bg-white border hover:border-slate-300 text-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-medium text-base transition-colors text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow">
                            Workflow ansehen
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-8 gap-y-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                            Keine App Installation
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                            100% DSGVO konform
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                            ERP Integration
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Sleek Phone Mockup -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative gs-reveal-hero perspective-1000" id="hero-phone-container">
                    <div class="absolute -right-12 top-20 w-32 h-32 bg-brand/10 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative mx-auto w-[320px] h-[650px] bg-slate-900 rounded-[3rem] p-2 shadow-2xl border-[6px] border-slate-800 transform rotate-[-2deg] hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out z-10">
                        
                        <!-- Screen -->
                        <div class="w-full h-full bg-[#ECE5DD] rounded-[2.25rem] overflow-hidden flex flex-col relative">
                            
                            <!-- Status Bar -->
                            <div class="h-7 bg-[#075E54] flex items-center justify-between px-4 text-white text-[10px]">
                                <span>9:41</span>
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
                                    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M1 9l2 2c4.97-4.97 13.03-4.97 18 0l2-2C16.93 2.93 7.08 2.93 1 9zm8 8l3 3 3-3c-1.65-1.66-4.34-1.66-6 0zm-4-4l2 2c2.76-2.76 7.24-2.76 10 0l2-2C15.14 9.14 8.87 9.14 5 13z"/></svg>
                                    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 18c4.97 0 9-4.03 9-9s-4.03-9-9-9-9 4.03-9 9 4.03 9 9 9zm0 2c-5.33 0-16 2.67-16 8v4h32v-4c0-5.33-10.67-8-16-8z"/></svg>
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 4h-3V2h-4v2H7v18h10V4zm-2 16H9V6h6v14z"/></svg>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- WhatsApp Header -->
                            <div class="bg-[#075E54] px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <button class="text-white/80 p-1">
                                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
                                </button>
                                <!-- WhatsApp Icon Avatar -->
                                <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-[#25D366] flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                                        <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex-1">
                                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">NexWorker</h3>
                                    <p class="text-[10px] text-white/70">online</p>
                                </div>
                                <button class="text-white/80 p-1.5">
                                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path></svg>
                                </button>
                                <button class="text-white/80 p-1.5">
                                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 5v.01M12 12v.01M12 19v.01M12 6a1 1 0 110-2 1 1 0 010 2zm0 7a1 1 0 110-2 1 1 0 010 2zm0 7a1 1 0 110-2 1 1 0 010 2z"></path></svg>
                                </button>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Chat Area -->
                            <div class="flex-1 overflow-hidden relative flex flex-col" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\'60\' height=\'60\' viewBox=\'0 0 60 60\' xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\'%3E%3Cg fill=\'%239C9C9C\' fill-opacity=\'0.08\'%3E%3Cpath d=\'M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z\'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E');">
                                
                                <!-- Date -->
                                <div class="flex justify-center my-3 relative z-10">
                                    <div class="bg-white/90 px-4 py-1 rounded-lg text-[11px] text-[#555] shadow-sm">Heute</div>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Messages -->
                                <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-3 pb-2 space-y-2 relative z-10">
                                    
                                    <!-- User message -->
                                    <div class="flex justify-end">
                                        <div class="max-w-[80%]">
                                            <div class="bg-[#DCF8C6] rounded-[7px] rounded-br-md px-3 py-1.5 shadow-sm">
                                                <p class="text-[13px] text-[#303030]">Guten Morgen! Bin auf der Baustelle Schulze. Material ist angekommen.</p>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="flex justify-end items-center gap-0.5 mt-0.5 px-1">
                                                <span class="text-[9px] text-[#999]">06:45</span>
                                                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#53bdeb]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 7l-1.41-1.41-6.34 6.34 1.41 1.41L18 7zm4.24-1.41L11.66 16.17 7.48 12l-1.41 1.41L11.66 19l12-12-1.42-1.41z"/></svg>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Bot message -->
                                    <div class="flex justify-start">
                                        <div class="max-w-[85%]">
                                            <div class="bg-white rounded-[7px] rounded-bl-md px-3 py-2 shadow-sm">
                                                <p class="text-[12px] text-emerald-600 font-semibold mb-1">✅ Start: 06:45</p>
                                                <p class="text-[12px] text-[#555]">👥 Thomas, Peter<br>📍 Baustelle Schulze</p>
                                            </div>
                                            <span class="text-[9px] text-[#999] ml-1">06:45</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- User message 2 -->
                                    <div class="flex justify-end">
                                        <div class="max-w-[80%]">
                                            <div class="bg-[#DCF8C6] rounded-[7px] rounded-br-md px-3 py-1.5 shadow-sm">
                                                <p class="text-[13px] text-[#303030]">2 Rollen Kabel 10mm². Geschätzt 240€.</p>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="flex justify-end items-center gap-0.5 mt-0.5 px-1">
                                                <span class="text-[9px] text-[#999]">11:20</span>
                                                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#53bdeb]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 7l-1.41-1.41-6.34 6.34 1.41 1.41L18 7zm4.24-1.41L11.66 16.17 7.48 12l-1.41 1.41L11.66 19l12-12-1.42-1.41z"/></svg>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Bot message 2 -->
                                    <div class="flex justify-start">
                                        <div class="max-w-[85%]">
                                            <div class="bg-white rounded-[7px] rounded-bl-md px-3 py-2 shadow-sm">
                                                <p class="text-[12px] text-emerald-600 font-semibold">📦 Material erfasst</p>
                                                <p class="text-[12px] text-[#555] mt-1">2x Kabel 10mm² – 240€</p>
                                            </div>
                                            <span class="text-[9px] text-[#999] ml-1">11:20</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- User message 3 -->
                                    <div class="flex justify-end">
                                        <div class="max-w-[75%]">
                                            <div class="bg-[#DCF8C6] rounded-[7px] rounded-br-md px-3 py-1.5 shadow-sm">
                                                <p class="text-[13px] text-[#303030]">Feierabend. 8,5 Stunden.</p>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="flex justify-end items-center gap-0.5 mt-0.5 px-1">
                                                <span class="text-[9px] text-[#999]">16:30</span>
                                                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#53bdeb]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18 7l-1.41-1.41-6.34 6.34 1.41 1.41L18 7zm4.24-1.41L11.66 16.17 7.48 12l-1.41 1.41L11.66 19l12-12-1.42-1.41z"/></svg>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Bot summary -->
                                    <div class="flex justify-start">
                                        <div class="max-w-[88%]">
                                            <div class="bg-white rounded-[7px] rounded-bl-md px-3 py-2 shadow-sm">
                                                <p class="text-[12px] text-[#075E54] font-semibold">📋 Tagesbericht</p>
                                                <p class="text-[11px] text-[#555] mt-1">⏱ 8,5h (Thomas, Peter)<br>📦 240€ Material<br>📍 Baustelle Schulze<br><span class="text-emerald-600">✓ Export bereit</span></p>
                                            </div>
                                            <span class="text-[9px] text-[#999] ml-1">16:30</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Input Area -->
                            <div class="bg-[#F0F0F0] px-3 py-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <button class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#606060]">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                                </button>
                                <button class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#606060]">
                                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                                </button>
                                <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-[13px] text-[#606060]">
                                    Nachricht
                                </div>
                                <button class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#075E54] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z"></path></svg>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Floating Badge -->
                    <div class="absolute -right-16 top-1/3 bg-white p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-floating gs-float border border-slate-100 hidden md:block z-20">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-2.5 rounded-xl text-brand">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">Zeiterfassung</p>
                                <p class="font-bold text-surface text-sm">Synchronisiert</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Platform Features -->
    <section id="was-ist" class="py-24 bg-slate-50 relative border-t border-slate-200">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20 gs-fade-up">
                <span class="text-brand font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mb-3 block">Plattform Architektur</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-surface mb-6 tracking-tight flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path></svg>
                    Was ist NexWorker?
                </h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 font-normal">
                    Keine isolierte Softwareinsel. NexWorker fungiert als intelligente Middleware, die in bekannten Messengern operiert und Daten strukturiert an Ihr Büro übergibt.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                
                <!-- Feature List -->
                <div class="space-y-4 gs-fade-up">
                    <div class="group flex gap-5 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:border-brand/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-1 bg-brand transform scale-y-0 group-hover:scale-y-100 transition-transform origin-top"></div>
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:text-brand group-hover:bg-brand/5 transition-colors border border-slate-100">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface mb-2">Semantische Sprachanalyse</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Gesprochene Notizen werden durch NLP (Natural Language Processing) transkribiert, kontextualisiert und strukturiert – selbst bei Umgebungslärm.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="group flex gap-5 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:border-brand/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden">
